  description="Expert Perlick repair for refrigerators, wine reserves, beverage centers, beer dispensers, undercounter refrigeration, refrigerator drawers, freezer drawers, outdoor refrigeration, and ice makers. Professional Perlick repair, maintenance, and installation support."
  ogImage="/perlick/perlick-repair-los-angeles-orange-county-ventura-county.webp"
